#it is possible to do maths with floats and integers
#it is not possible to do maths with strings or characters
#example

num1 = 20 #int
num2 = 30 #int
total = num1 + num2
print(total)

num3 = 20.1 #float
num4 = 30.9 #float
total = num3 + num4
print(total)

num5 = "20" #strings
num6 = "30" #strings
total = num5 + num6
print(total)
#you cannot add strings or characters
#Instead, the adds symbol glues them together
#But we don't call it glue, we call it concentration
